    "notes": "Route 32 is 20x90 tiles — one of the longest routes in Johto. The left (west) side has a long lake/pond (surfable). Ruins of Alph gate is in the upper-left at y2-3. Pokemon Center sits around y73 on the west side. Union Cave entrance at y79. Coordinates and NPC positions are taken directly from pokecrystal object_event entries. Tile layout is a schematic approximation; actual block pattern comes from Route32.blk."
