  "notes": "Route 32 is the longest route in Johto at 10x45 blocks (20x90 tiles). It runs south from Violet City through a region of tall grass and a long western lake before reaching Union Cave. Key features: (1) Cool Trainer M blocks entry without Zephyr Badge; (2) Ruins of Alph gate access in the upper-left; (3) Pokemon Center mid-route where the Fishing Guru gives the Old Rod; (4) 8 trainers including 3 fishers; (5) Frieda of Friday Friday-only NPC; (6) Slowpoke Tail salesman cutscene; (7) 4 items (2 visible, 2 hidden). Ekans is Gold-exclusive in grass. Pokecrystal source: maps/Route32.asm. Route 33 is NOT a direct connection — Union Cave separates them."
}
